                                                                                                                                                                                                     Pavlyuchenko for Spurs
            IN amp; OUT                
	 Roman Pavlyuchenko has claimed that he is joining Tottenham Hotspur. The Russia forward, 26, has not travelled with Spartak Moscow for the second leg of their Champions League third qualifying round tie against Dynamo Kiev.         
	Robinho deal         
	 Chelsea are edging closer to agreeing a fee in the region of 29 million for Robinho after holding talks with Real Madrid on Tuesday. Real hope to sign a replacement, but Valencia have rejected their offer for David Villa, the Spain forward.                                                                                                                            
